metadata.name: Lying To Herself
metadata.description:
She felt that familiar feeling. 
The heaviness and blur as she once again lied to herself.
Told herself that everything would be alright. 

Truth and Lies. We use both to control Ourselves, Strangers, Friends, and Lovers.
